summary: This is a grand jury subpoena issued to the VI Division of Banking, Insurance and Financial Regulations, served on April 8, 2020, with a return received in 2020. It is part of a sealed grand jury proceeding related to case 196D-SJ-3262541-GJ.

keyFacts: A grand jury subpoena was issued to the VI Division of Banking, Insurance and Financial Regulations, indicating an investigation into financial records.
The subpoena was served on April 8, 2020, and its return was received in 2020, showing ongoing grand jury activity.
The document is part of a sealed grand jury proceeding under case ID 196D-SJ-3262541-GJ, with strict confidentiality rules under Federal Rule of Criminal Procedure 6(e)(3).
